release_note: Dear users we are thrilled to announce a new update to our app! In this version we ve introduced a section dedicated to affirmations that we hope will inspire you and boost your self confidence every day. Additionally we ve made a series of visual enhancements for an even more comfortable user experience. Your feedback is extremely important to us so please do not hesitate to share your impressions and suggestions. With love the PSY team.

Dear our users in the new update we have improved the design and also added fixes. We always care about your comfort and try to give you the best experience using our app. We look forward to your feedback to make our app even better for you! Thank you for choosing us! PSY Team.

We re excited to introduce our new and amazing update! We now offer special courses designed by therapists to help you care for your psychological well being. Each course includes daily tasks and recommendations that assist you in overcoming various challenges and stressful situations. Choose the course that meets your needs and goals. Take care of yourself and your mental health and we ll be right beside you to support you through the journey. With love the Psy team!
